{"tid":927814,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【飯碗不保？】緊隨Amazon Go其後，7-Eleven打算推出無人便利店！","createTime":"2018-12-04T11:50:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-05T07:21:06.000Z","uid":212399,"like":6,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"5aa3cc242255e74ab0d74c5a90ebc4004de25e9c","tid":927814,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T11:50:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s3-ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/techstart.presslogic.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/amazongoandseven.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs3-ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com%2Ftechstart.presslogic.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F12%2Famazongoandseven.jpg&h=ceb14d55&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n亞馬遜推出無人商店Amazon Go後，7-Eleven都急起直追。據《日經亞洲評論》報道，7-Eleven正在日本測試新的概念商店，期望將來不再需要收銀員。這些新店在7-Eleven的店面總數中佔比很小，並將使用人臉識別來認證消費者並完成結賬。<br />\n<img src=\"https://s3-ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/techstart.presslogic.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/shutterstock_253195477.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs3-ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com%2Ftechstart.presslogic.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F12%2Fshutterstock_253195477.jpg&h=e8e3a3e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n對美國和日本的7-Eleven加盟商來說，這肯定是個好消息，因為日本有勞動短缺的問題，而美國的加盟商則臨最低工資上漲。對收銀員來說，這當然是一條壞消息，因為他們的工作可能會被取代。<br />\n<img src=\"https://s3-ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/techstart.presslogic.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/shutterstock_764823805.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs3-ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com%2Ftechstart.presslogic.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F12%2Fshutterstock_764823805.jpg&h=c4c050d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n此前不久，亞馬遜推出了Amazon Go無人便利店，改變了傳統的便利店模式。Amazon Go便利店沒有收銀員，全部通過現代科技來監控客流和購買行為，對7-Eleven構成挑戰。<br />\n<img src=\"https://s3-ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/techstart.presslogic.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/shutterstock_1128625253.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs3-ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com%2Ftechstart.presslogic.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F12%2Fshutterstock_1128625253.jpg&h=bbaff7da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n其中一個挑戰是購物速度：消費者無需排隊結賬，可隨時進出商店。另外，在這個最低工資標準不斷上漲的年代，與招聘、監控和管理勞動力有關的成本都可以節省下來。此外，亞馬遜旗下的全食超市還可以與Amazon Go協同運營，由前者負責準備食物，後者負責出售。因此，亞馬遜進軍便利店領域相信對7-Eleven的利潤構成壓力，而連鎖便利店通常都是靠微利營運，故此，削減一兩個人手對便利店能否賺錢有很大影響。7-Eleven別無選擇只能追隨亞馬遜所引領的趨勢。<br />\n<a href=\"https://businessfocus.presslogic.com/2018/12/03/article/85022\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbusinessfocus.presslogic.com%2F2018%2F12%2F03%2Farticle%2F85022&d=wy78JA13ImWpYiwIp9yh8%2F755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=67f980c8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://businessfocus.presslogic.com/2018/12/03/article/85022</a>"},{"pid":"0546e00214067a86086154b5752101d6069f7246","tid":927814,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T11:52:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a20dacd64cd5154f1e9d26a94c7ef7883800b32","tid":927814,"uid":17646,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T11:52:20.000Z","msg":"香港如果有，又係露宿者霸住"},{"pid":"8310acdcd6502efa9e7072783eb495b10dec09ac","tid":927814,"uid":83623,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T11:58:23.000Z","msg":"望返Amazon go，比超市只係少啲人手，入面仲係好多人做嘢，cashierless 主要改善購物體驗同增加無形消費"},{"pid":"dbf4bee5caf36f60d8c00f9babc5a6e82fe8a614","tid":927814,"uid":28831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1a20dacd64cd5154f1e9d26a94c7ef7883800b32","tid":927814,"uid":17646,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T11:52:20.000Z","msg":"香港如果有，又係露宿者霸住"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T12:02:06.000Z","msg":"香港迫到咁間舖實長期爆滿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc4bd8b1cdcd517d355cceb966a251556349aaf0","tid":927814,"uid":18948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T12:03:26.000Z","msg":"兩日後執笠"},{"pid":"c4b48e69fbfcd624aa48db25dbc02ed665e54f11","tid":927814,"